blessing the bread, and the wine,

00:33:33.020 --> 00:33:36.100
and your children every
single Friday night.

00:33:36.100 --> 00:33:41.200
That is a good habit of
mind to get into, I think.

00:33:41.200 --> 00:33:42.500
&gt;&gt; STEVEN KNAPP: What else?

00:33:42.500 --> 00:33:45.320
